@startuml
participant "PaymentServiceImpl" as PaymentService
participant "EmailServiceImpl" as EmailService
participant "JavaMailSender" as MailSender

PaymentService -> PaymentService: 1. handleVnPayReturn() → responseCode=="00"
PaymentService -> PaymentService: 2. Cập nhật payment & booking
PaymentService -> PaymentService: 3. Tính earnedPoint + update tier
PaymentService -> EmailService: 4. sendBookingConfirmationEmail(customer, booking, payment)
EmailService -> EmailService: 5. Tạo MimeMessage + build HTML (room table)
EmailService -> MailSender: 6. send(mimeMessage)
MailSender --> EmailService: 7. Email sent successfully
EmailService --> PaymentService: 8. Hoàn tất gửi mail
@enduml